    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this car to believe it. It\u2019s an absolute gem and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014not a single scratch or ding, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for a new home. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly pristine condition, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
